{"type": "article", "id": 50190, "title": "传复星集团成功竞购 Lanvin，以及，东京小学推出 Armani 校服 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-02-12T04:19:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1530, "name": "Lanvin"}, {"id": 6419, "name": "Armani"}, {"id": 8634, "name": "Supreme"}, {"id": 1831, "name": "复星"}, {"id": 354, "name": "阿里巴巴"}, {"id": 33916, "name": "居然之家"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180212120750xFJ8qhASdEkzwMGT.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/mergers-acquisitions/alibaba-easyhome-invest-home-retail-1202551762/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>54.5 亿人民币，阿里巴巴入股居然之家</strong></a> | 阿里巴巴集团正式宣布，投资 54.5 亿人民币，持有居然之家 15％ 的股份，将运用集团的会员体系、云计算、企业服务体系及物流平台，支持居然之家在中国 223 家门店的数字化升级。</p><p><a href=\"http://uk.fashionnetwork.com/news/EXCLUSIVE-Fosun-International-wins-auction-for-Lanvin,946513.html#.WoEQVZP1UzU\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>传：复星集团赢得 Lanvin 竞购</strong></a> | 外媒透露，中国复星集团打败卡塔尔王室投资公司 Mayhoola，赢得了法国品牌 Lanvin 的竞购。上周五双方签署了协议，预计本周，Lanvin 的员工将会收到确切的消息。一位消息人士称，这笔交易中复星集团将向 Lanvin 投资超过 1 亿欧元，并向新控股股东发行新股，台湾富商王效兰将失去对 Lanvin 的控制权。 </p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/fashion-show-review/alexander-wangs-ceo-shitkickers\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alexander Wang </a>最后一次参加纽约时装周，他塑造了干练的女 CEO 形象。 </p><p>模特们戴上了与 Gentle Monster 合作的怪异墨镜，穿上了皮裙、丝袜，不规则剪裁的衬衫...有几套装扮看起来还很像是《黑客帝国》女主角。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802121201451NjZDyH7KugaPecB.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802121201464kTeI13RAHpFqNgx.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120146mliMnwjGL1YBza3q.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120146naykdmeDQfT48hvK.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802121201467TWDmwRC34tjhKVg.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120146UdJmYkA1ctew53vn.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120146zpU2TQPumr7t0Ecd.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120146KUB57Zyq2GEMcCLt.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802121201468BwYTLxMPfGc6Xdj.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120146z6TheJZfKv3jGbPy.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120146KREjtBZvwAmICSlG.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120146opySzAZehxGmcwdW.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120146sIvVgELBCnhm7eiA.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120146P1tfc4kTey6OLsYj.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120147HMhOe0p61ztXVKnl.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120147PCqAtGjOicwF1ENs.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120147wWTnRXz4DgjPQmJM.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120147zVceaUl2yuw763vr.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120147TVsERZCHBcuza5Gg.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120147zE6N4c9adMru1WPl.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120147CXfv18ny2mtYp0Zi.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802121201482D4NK6e3EfryaUBc.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120148OcJRAnpkBGuwagbK.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120148z87xsqbe0PEDrBS3.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120148Ze4GWSRlDwA7bxdN.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120148YgF2PEVM7n9jQvxN.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120148czeaCE8ZxDoBiHuk.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120148zkO0L6xlmB38VAFa.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120148PsRk3NOMUhVuaicG.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>东京银座的<a href=\"https://popbee.com/fashion/fashion-news/armani-uniforms-in-tokyo-grade-school/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Taimei Elementary School</a>，计划在今年四月新学年开始时，为学生们提供由 Giorgio Armani 设计的校服，校长和田利次认为这是“符合银座学校标准”的服装，但因为每套校服收费 8 万日元，很多家长表示难以负担。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120300d4XTGpR5PrZDzSmQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebae.com/2018/2/supreme-stern-pinball-machine-video\" rel=\"nofollow\">Supreme 与游戏公司 Stern 合作，宣布推出弹球机</a>。 </p><p>从 Instagram 发布的预览视频来看，这个联名款弹球机全面覆盖了 Supreme 标志性的红白 logo 图案。另外，Supreme 的 2018 春夏系列将于美国时间 2 月 12 日正式推出。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120312I7jJr8L3odxnfRDF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/article/2018-02-12/moncler-genius/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Moncler </a>最近在东京开展了一系列神秘的广告活动。 </p><p>在松屋银座、表参道交叉口，以及成田空港这些人流量大的地方，Moncler 的新广告牌以“A NEW CHAPTER OF CREATIVITY”和“GENIUS AT WORK”为标语，出现了仿佛被冻住的八个人和一只动物，人们纷纷猜测出现在广告牌中的人到底是谁，但直到 2 月 20 日，Moncler 才会揭晓这个悬念。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120332ZYAHowhbykXrIeim.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120332ZckRU0E3uI6gJzBD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802121203377Oqb2P0TuC9FHxNw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>这个月 17 日，<a href=\"https://hypebae.com/2018/2/kendall-jenner-danielle-cathari-adidas-originals-tracksuit-campaign-release-date\" rel=\"nofollow\">adidas Originals 将发布与 DaniëlleCathari 的合作系列</a>。 </p><p>该系列包括色彩丰富的运动服套装、紧身衣，外套和裙子，adidas 经典的三条杠 logo 也有了新的诠释。来看看 Kendall Jenner 的演绎：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802121200161PlJmUKDu2Y4eWpz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120016l4sxXVHKLje9v7CN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120016BEKm2T1LpRhcAXi6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120016NlOUI0pyXRjHMmAx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120016w9bhPnlsuZJ8qSCF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120016cA6jThJGfIPVbOBt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120017CmxWShMfdu90LE3N.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120017sc3rMSDdXkJ5LNnV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802121200173ns68jXNPlSWTdIh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180212120017Zs9i7gEJbImcu15Y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.334000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：Supreme</p>"}